{"arkId":"cl010156724","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010156724","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"tess\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"tess\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Romain Imp\u00e9rial (-63 - 324)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-63,"endYear":324,"imprecision":"","text":"Romain Imp\u00e9rial","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"AO 32507","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Pr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Cette petite tess\u00e8re carr\u00e9e porte sur la face A le buste d\u2019une divinit\u00e9 coiff\u00e9e du kalathos. Il porte au-dessus de chaque \u00e9paule un serpent. Sur la face B est repr\u00e9sent\u00e9 un scorpion. L\u2019association de cette divinit\u00e9 avec les serpents et le scorpion fait penser que la divinit\u00e9 repr\u00e9sent\u00e9e n\u2019est autre que Shadrafa, un dieu gu\u00e9risseur, associ\u00e9 sp\u00e9cifiquement \u00e0 Palmyre \u00e0 ces deux animaux. Une st\u00e8le du British Museum le repr\u00e9sente en armure avec une lance, aussi accompagn\u00e9 d\u2019un scorpion et d\u2019un serpent. La d\u00e9dicace y identifie sp\u00e9cifiquement Shadrafa.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,2","displayDimension":"1,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"1","displayDimension":"1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : terre cuite","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOf